-index-card__title\">中途採用</div>\n<p class=\"recruit-index-card__text\">正社員、契約社員「アンカーキャスト」をご希望の方</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"recruit-index-card__item\"><a href=\"https://kuronekoyamato.saiyo-job.jp/yx9p/recruit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"recruit-index-card__type\">\n<div class=\"recruit-index-card__head\">\n<figure class=\"recruit-index-card__image--ptw\"><picture> <source srcset=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_guide_ic03.webp\" type=\"image/webp\"> <source srcset=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_guide_ic03.png\" type=\"image/png\"> <img src=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_guide_ic03.png\" alt=\"\"> </picture></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-index-card__body\">\n<div class=\"recruit-index-card__title--small\">パート・アルバイト採用</div>\n<p class=\"recruit-index-card__text\">パート・アルバイト勤務をご希望の方</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n<div class=\"recruit-index-card__item\"><a href=\"https://kuronekoyamato.saiyo-job.jp/s9h5/recruit/challenged/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"recruit-index-card__type\">\n<div class=\"recruit-index-card__head\">\n<figure class=\"recruit-index-card__image--challenge\"><picture> <source srcset=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_guide_ic04.webp\" type=\"image/webp\"> <source srcset=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_guide_ic04.png\" type=\"image/png\"> <img src=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_guide_ic04.png\" alt=\"\"> </picture></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-index-card__body\">\n<div class=\"recruit-index-card__title\">障がい者採用</div>\n<p class=\"recruit-index-card__text\">当社の採用方針のほか、募集職種や応募方法などをご案内しています。</p>\n</div>\n</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-index-visual__image\">\n<figure><picture> <source srcset=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_visual_im01_pc.webp\" type=\"image/webp\"> <source srcset=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_visual_im01_pc.jpg\" type=\"image/jpg\"> <img src=\"/ytc/corp/recruit/img/index_visual_im01_pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"util-sp-hidden\"> </picture> <picture> <source srcset=\"/ytc/corp/rec